      "text": "Real time game leaderboard",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Real time game leaderboard",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ofjdbBEpNa3WoL0p_dK7u",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 310,
      "y": 211.5,
      "width": 632.6795654296875,
      "height": 1300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bi4",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 964135077,
      "version": 948,
      "versionNonce": 454251525,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1783773563428,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Clarifications:\n\nq. single game?\nyes, assume game like chess\nif time permits we will have more games\n2 player game: yes\n\nq. how a leader is defined\nuser gets a score when the win a match.\nlets say +1, and leaderboard gets adjusted\n\nq. real time?\nyes\n\nq. imp features:\nwe get scores of a match and winner and loser\nwe create a leaderboard from the points\nuser can view leaderboard with top 10 scores\nuser can view theri position and see 4 positions above and below\n\nq. scale?\n5 m DAU\n\nq. what ahppens when 2 player have same score:\nsame rank\n\nFunctional req:\n- Score match results and craete leaderboard:\nwe get scores of a match and winner and loser\nwe create a leaderboard from the points\n- View leaderboard\nuser can view leaderboard with top 10 scores\nuser can view theri position and see 4 positions above and below\n\nNFR:\nAvailability\nrelibility and fault tolerent\nscalable\nCorrectness\n\nback of the envelope calc:\n5 m DAU * 20 matches a day\n= 100m matches a day\n= 100m/ 10^5\n= 1000 writes per second\n\nReads:\n10m DAU * 50 \n= 500 m reads per day\n= 500m / 10^5\n= 5000 rps\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Clarifications:\n\nq. single game?\nyes, assume game like chess\nif time permits we will have more games\n2 player game: yes\n\nq. how a leader is defined\nuser gets a score when the win a match.\nlets say +1, and leaderboard gets adjusted\n\nq. real time?\nyes\n\nq. imp features:\nwe get scores of a match and winner and loser\nwe create a leaderboard from the points\nuser can view leaderboard with top 10 scores\nuser can view theri position and see 4 positions above and below\n\nq. scale?\n5 m DAU\n\nq. what ahppens when 2 player have same score:\nsame rank\n\nFunctional req:\n- Score match results and craete leaderboard:\nwe get scores of a match and winner and loser\nwe create a leaderboard from the points\n- View leaderboard\nuser can view leaderboard with top 10 scores\nuser can view theri position and see 4 positions above and below\n\nNFR:\nAvailability\nrelibility and fault tolerent\nscalable\nCorrectness\n\nback of the envelope calc:\n5 m DAU * 20 matches a day\n= 100m matches a day\n= 100m/ 10^5\n= 1000 writes per second\n\nReads:\n10m DAU * 50 \n= 500 m reads per day\n= 500m / 10^5\n= 5000 rps\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
